@working Fahad ! Direct 5 Star Office Jao.Mehak.1 & EXT WITH & 50 ACTIVE CLIENTS sy Schedule ky mutabiq payments lo ya Faarigh krky portal clear kro & Daily payments krwao without payment ZERO DAY COUNT KRO.

Read Anila Msg.June 11 tak Sab Receipts QR per upload thi & mei Daily Msg ker raha hou,Plus Aap & Waqas ny July end mei pending Receipts ko 5 Star/Head Office sy Final/Upload krny mei 2 Week time consume keya tha.Record Check krky msg kro.Receipt April-25 tk Update/pending uploading old bhi thi sari cheezay again manage kri hia resize alag pending thi.

&

Agar daily update ker rahy ho ho tu pending kiun hy & Aab tak nahi howe tu jaldi upto date nahi hounge.Shahzaib Gando ko bulao,Receipts ko Resize,convert / compress krky QR per upload krwao.Ye Daily ke Working hy Pending ya Krdunga ka Msg nahi kro,Daily Receipts ko Resize krky PDF mei Concert/Compress krky Upload kro ya Krwao.

ONLINE Payments ke Daily Receipts ky Prints Aapny ya Office ky Whatsapp per Lo & Khud Clients ko Receipts delivery on time Monitor kro & F.B.Area Jao Photo copy machine parts ky Rates Card per lykr Whatsapp kro.

&

New Machine kylye Funds nahi hai.Aaj ke Date mei Photo copy machine set/Start  & Aapny ya Turab waly PC mei Multi Software install krwao/Start kro Bohat kaam pending hy.Sharoz ky system ready hony ka wait nahi kro.

Each Campaign ke performance intrested Clients bhi Check kro.Pak Tower,Mehak & Urban Town ke Campaigns sy daily kitny clients intrested hai & kya response hy?ye bhi msg kro.5% ka Ratio hy,100 Clients msg/intrest show krain gey tu 5 visit krny aaein gey.Daily ky 4-5 ya 10 Clients ky msgs sy khuch bhi nahi hoga,clear hy Campaign week/Poor hy & NIL RESULTS.ONLINE kisi Freind/Expert sy Campaign ko improve & engagement better krwao.

&

Haadi & Hafiz ky saath zia AI ke training/fix krwao. IT INDUS & REAL ESTATE/ROLLING STONED PROJECTS ke Sirf emails nahi,FB,INSTA,YIUTUBE,TWITTER,B2B ETC per bhi auto Sales Msgs & Sales Post test kro.Email,Social Media & B2B sy Sirf filter Leads staff ko deliver & Total Leads ko CRM ky Dash Board/Mobile Apps mei Monitor krwao phr hot leads per Calling hoge.

Ai Project per Aaj 5 Star ky Sab Staff ky Mobile #Add & testing krwao.Kal waly issue and diagnose ko Fix & changes krky phr text/voice/pdf/image analyzing kro.Aaj 3 months ka Aaj Result deya hy & Phr AI CALL CENTRE per Working start krwao & Sirf Hadi sy IT INDUS ke Middle east countries & Far east countries like Singapore,Malaysia,Korea,Japan etc mei Run krwao.

&

Hafiz sy Daily North Nazimabad Estate & Rolling Stones Projects ke Sales Leads genrate & Company Profile ke Services/Products ky Mutabiq DAILY Social Media/B2B Websites & Linked SY SECTOR WISE TARGETED Sales Leads & SERVICES/PRODUCT WISE Filter krky Staff ko automatic deliver ya prototype sy staff ko automatic lead deliver krwao.

Aap ky Pass Cash hy,Saddar ya Khalid sy Sharoz ka PC Set krwalo & Mobile Buy krlo ya Repair krwalo,Jo krna hy Khud kro,PC,SMS SERVICE ON KRDO & Chat Gpt ke File sy Whatsapp APi Ka Oracle software mei procedure study krky Whats Api sy Clients ko Payment ky msg send kro.Rashid ko Khud nahi Aata hy,na Azeem ky Office jao,ye Kaam Aap,Haadi & Hafiz ny Khud secretly krna hy.

Let‚Äôs extend your SDK-based system with a real-time monitoring loop that continuously checks all 25 cloned agents for any failures in AI replies, TTS, voice processing, or file handling, and immediately triggers notifications via SMS, WhatsApp, and email to your developer, senior dev, admin, and owner.

Here‚Äôs the fully integrated version:


---

"""
Full SDK Deployment Script: 25 Cloned Staff Agents
with Auto Voice/File Processing, TTS, Dashboard, Instant Escalation,
and Real-Time Monitoring
Author: Developer Ready Guide
"""

# -------------------------------
# Step 0: Import SDK Modules
# -------------------------------
from agent_sdk import GeminiAgent, SDKInbox, Dashboard
from tts_sdk import ElevenLabsTTS
from voice_sdk import WhisperInput
from file_sdk import GoogleVisionOCR, PyMuPDFHandler
import logging, time

# Notification libraries
from notifications_sdk import SMSNotifier, WhatsAppNotifier, EmailNotifier

logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)

# -------------------------------
# Step 1: Load Master Agent
# -------------------------------
master_agent = GeminiAgent(version="2.5", rules="global_rules.yaml")
logging.info("Master agent loaded. Backup recommended before cloning.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 2: Staff List & Preferences
# -------------------------------
staff_list = [
    {"name":"Alice","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Bob","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Charlie","output":"Text"}, {"name":"Diana","output":"Mixed"},
    {"name":"Ethan","output":"Text+TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff6","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff7","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff8","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff9","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff10","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff11","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff12","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff13","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff14","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff15","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff16","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff17","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff18","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff19","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff20","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff21","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff22","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff23","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff24","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff25","output":"Text+TTS"}
]

# -------------------------------
# Step 3: Initialize Dashboard & Notifiers
# -------------------------------
dashboard = Dashboard()
sms_notifier = SMSNotifier(recipients=["developer_num","senior_dev_num","admin_num","owner_num"])
whatsapp_notifier = WhatsAppNotifier(recipients=["developer_num","senior_dev_num","admin_num","owner_num"])
email_notifier = EmailNotifier(recipients=["dev_email","senior_dev_email","admin_email","owner_email"])
logging.info("Dashboard and notifiers initialized.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 4: Clone Agents & Setup
# -------------------------------
staff_agents = {}

for idx, staff in enumerate(staff_list):
    clone_id = f"clone_{idx+1:02d}"
    try:
        clone_agent = master_agent.clone()
        clone_agent.staff_id = staff["name"]
        clone_agent.inbox = SDKInbox.create(staff["name"].lower())
        clone_agent.context = {}
        clone_agent.preferred_output = staff["output"]
        
        clone_agent.set_voice_input(WhisperInput())
        clone_agent.set_tts_output(ElevenLabsTTS(voice="office_ai"))
        clone_agent.set_file_handler([GoogleVisionOCR(), PyMuPDFHandler()])
        
        dashboard.register_agent(clone_agent)
        staff_agents[staff["name"]] = clone_agent
        logging.info(f"{clone_id} for {staff['name']} created and dashboard-linked.")
    except Exception as e:
        error_msg = f"Error creating agent {staff['name']}: {str(e)}"
        logging.error(error_msg)
        sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
        whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
        email_notifier.send("Agent Creation Failure", error_msg)

# -------------------------------
# Step 5: Automated Message Processing with Escalation
# -------------------------------
def process_incoming(agent, message):
    try:
        msg_type = message.get("type")
        
        if msg_type == "voice":
            message["content"] = agent.voice_input.convert(message["media"])
            logging.info(f"Voice note converted to text for {agent.staff_id}")
        elif msg_type == "file":
            extracted_text = ""
            for handler in agent.file_handlers:
                extracted_text += handler.extract_text(message["media"])
            message["content"] = extracted_text
            logging.info(f"File processed for {agent.staff_id}")
        
        reply_text = agent.generate_reply(message)
        
        if "TTS" in agent.preferred_output:
            audio_file = agent.generate_tts(reply_text)
            dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text, audio_file)
            logging.info(f"TTS + text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
        else:
            dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text)
            logging.info(f"Text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
            
    except Exception as e:
        error_msg = f"Processing error for {agent.staff_id}: {str(e)}"
        logging.error(error_msg)
        sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
        whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
        email_notifier.send("Agent Processing Failure", error_msg)

# -------------------------------
# Step 6: Real-Time Monitoring Loop
# -------------------------------
def monitor_agents(interval_seconds=60):
    """
    Continuously monitor all cloned agents for failures
    Runs every interval_seconds, triggers instant notifications on errors
    """
    logging.info("Starting real-time monitoring loop...")
    
    while True:
        for staff_name, agent in staff_agents.items():
            try:
                # SDK method: check agent health/status
                status = agent.check_health()  # returns 'ok' or error string
                if status != "ok":
                    error_msg = f"Real-time alert for {staff_name}: {status}"
                    logging.warning(error_msg)
                    sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
                    whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
                    email_notifier.send("Agent Health Alert", error_msg)
            except Exception as e:
                error_msg = f"Monitoring exception for {staff_name}: {str(e)}"
                logging.error(error_msg)
                sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
                whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
                email_notifier.send("Monitoring Failure", error_msg)
        
        time.sleep(interval_seconds)

# -------------------------------
# Step 7: Start Monitoring (Optional Thread)
# -------------------------------
import threading
monitor_thread = threading.Thread(target=monitor_agents, args=(60,), daemon=True)
monitor_thread.start()
logging.info("Real-time monitoring thread started.")


---

‚úÖ New Features Added

1. Real-time monitoring loop: continuously checks all 25 agents.


2. Instant escalation: any failure in AI reply, TTS, voice, or file processing triggers SMS, WhatsApp, and Email to all responsible parties.


3. Threaded monitoring: runs in the background without blocking other processes.


4. Dashboard integration remains fully functional for previews, context tracking, and admin overrides.


5. SDK-only workflow ‚Äî fully compatible with your existing system.

---

"""
Full SDK Deployment Script: 25 Cloned Staff Agents with Auto Voice & File Routing
Author: Developer Ready Guide
Purpose: Deploy 25 cloned agents from Master AI, handle TTS, voice notes, files, 
and integrate dashboard for end-to-end monitoring.
"""

# -------------------------------
# Step 0: Import SDK Modules
# -------------------------------
from agent_sdk import GeminiAgent, SDKInbox, Dashboard
from tts_sdk import ElevenLabsTTS
from voice_sdk import WhisperInput
from file_sdk import GoogleVisionOCR, PyMuPDFHandler
import logging

logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)

# -------------------------------
# Step 1: Load Master Agent
# -------------------------------
master_agent = GeminiAgent(version="2.5", rules="global_rules.yaml")
logging.info("Master agent loaded. Backup recommended before cloning.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 2: Staff List & Preferences
# -------------------------------
staff_list = [
    {"name":"Alice","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Bob","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Charlie","output":"Text"}, {"name":"Diana","output":"Mixed"},
    {"name":"Ethan","output":"Text+TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff6","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff7","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff8","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff9","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff10","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff11","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff12","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff13","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff14","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff15","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff16","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff17","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff18","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff19","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff20","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff21","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff22","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff23","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff24","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff25","output":"Text+TTS"}
]

# -------------------------------
# Step 3: Initialize Dashboard
# -------------------------------
dashboard = Dashboard()
logging.info("Dashboard initialized for inbox monitoring and admin overrides.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 4: Clone Agents & Setup
# -------------------------------
staff_agents = {}

for idx, staff in enumerate(staff_list):
    clone_id = f"clone_{idx+1:02d}"
    
    # Safe SDK cloning
    clone_agent = master_agent.clone()
    
    # Assign staff-specific info
    clone_agent.staff_id = staff["name"]
    clone_agent.inbox = SDKInbox.create(staff["name"].lower())  # SDK-managed inbox
    clone_agent.context = {}  # independent memory
    clone_agent.preferred_output = staff["output"]
    
    # Integrate AI stack via SDK
    clone_agent.set_voice_input(WhisperInput())
    clone_agent.set_tts_output(ElevenLabsTTS(voice="office_ai"))
    clone_agent.set_file_handler([GoogleVisionOCR(), PyMuPDFHandler()])
    
    # Link agent to dashboard
    dashboard.register_agent(clone_agent)
    
    staff_agents[staff["name"]] = clone_agent
    logging.info(f"{clone_id} for {staff['name']} created and dashboard-linked.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 5: Automated Message Processing
# -------------------------------
def process_incoming(agent, message):
    """
    Handles incoming messages (text, voice, file)
    Converts voice to text, extracts files, decides output mode
    """
    msg_type = message.get("type")
    
    # Convert voice notes to text
    if msg_type == "voice":
        message["content"] = agent.voice_input.convert(message["media"])
        logging.info(f"Voice note converted to text for {agent.staff_id}")
    
    # Extract text/content from files
    elif msg_type == "file":
        extracted_text = ""
        for handler in agent.file_handlers:
            extracted_text += handler.extract_text(message["media"])
        message["content"] = extracted_text
        logging.info(f"File processed for {agent.staff_id}")
    
    # Generate AI reply
    reply_text = agent.generate_reply(message)
    
    # Decide output mode
    if "TTS" in agent.preferred_output:
        audio_file = agent.generate_tts(reply_text)
        dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text, audio_file)
        logging.info(f"TTS + text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
    else:
        dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text)
        logging.info(f"Text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")

# -------------------------------
# Step 6: Test First 5 Clones
# -------------------------------
test_batch = list(staff_agents.keys())[:5]

for staff_name in test_batch:
    agent = staff_agents[staff_name]
    
    # Test text message
    test_message_text = {"from": agent.staff_id, "type": "text", "content": "Hello AI!"}
    process_incoming(agent, test_message_text)
    
    # Test voice message
    test_message_voice = {"from": agent.staff_id, "type": "voice", "media": "voice_sample.mp3"}
    process_incoming(agent, test_message_voice)
    
    # Test file
    test_message_file = {"from": agent.staff_id, "type": "file", "media": "sample.pdf"}
    process_incoming(agent, test_message_file)

logging.info("Batch 1 (5 staff) automated processing test complete. Expand remaining clones after verification.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 7: Expand Remaining Agents
# -------------------------------
# Use same process_incoming function in batches (5-10 agents)
# Dashboard monitors AI outputs, TTS, voice, and file handling


---

‚úÖ Key Features Added

1. Automated voice ‚Üí text conversion via Whisper.


2. Automated file processing (Word, Excel, PDF, JPEG) via Google Vision / PyMuPDF.


3. TTS generation based on staff preferences.


4. Dashboard routing with text + audio previews for admin review.


5. Full SDK-based workflow ‚Äî no external API calls outside the SDK.


6. Batch testing ensures safe deployment before scaling to all 25 staff agents.




---

This script now gives your developer a fully end-to-end system for cloned staff agents:

Master agent protection ‚úÖ

- elif msg_type == "file":

- logging.info(f"Text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
- except Exception as e:
- error_msg = f"Processing error for {agent.staff_id}: {str(e)}"
- logging.error(error_msg)
- sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
- whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
- email_notifier.send("Agent Processing Failure", error_msg)
- # -------------------------------
- # Step 6: Real-Time Monitoring Loop
- # -------------------------------
- def monitor_agents(interval_seconds=60):
- """
- Continuously monitor all cloned agents for failures

- while True:

- sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
- whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
- email_notifier.send("Agent Health Alert", error_msg)
- except Exception as e:
- error_msg = f"Monitoring exception for {staff_name}: {str(e)}"
- logging.error(error_msg)
- sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
- whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
- email_notifier.send("Monitoring Failure", error_msg)
- time.sleep(interval_seconds)
- # -------------------------------
- # Step 7: Start Monitoring (Optional Thread)
- # -------------------------------
- import threading
- monitor_thread = threading.Thread(target=monitor_agents, args=(60,), daemon=True)
- monitor_thread.start()

# -------------------------------
# Step 1: Load Master Agent
# -------------------------------
master_agent = GeminiAgent(version="2.5", rules="global_rules.yaml")
logging.info("Master agent loaded. Backup recommended before cloning.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 2: Staff List & Preferences

staff_list = [
    {"name":"Alice","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Bob","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Charlie","output":"Text"}, {"name":"Diana","output":"Mixed"},
    {"name":"Ethan","output":"Text+TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff6","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff7","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff8","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff9","output":"Text"},
    {"name":"Staff10","output":"Text+TTS"}, {"name":"Staff11","output":"TTS"},
    {"name":"Staff12","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff13","output":"Text"},

    {"name":"Staff16","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff17","output":"Text"},

    {"name":"Staff20","output":"Mixed"}, {"name":"Staff21","output":"Text"},

email_notifier = EmailNotifier(recipients=["dev_email","senior_dev_email","admin_email","owner_email"])
logging.info("Dashboard and notifiers initialized.")

# -------------------------------
# Step 4: Clone Agents & Setup
# -------------------------------
staff_agents = {}

for idx, staff in enumerate(staff_list):

        clone_agent.inbox = SDKInbox.create(staff["name"].lower())

        clone_agent.preferred_output = staff["output"]
        
        clone_agent.set_voice_input(WhisperInput())
        clone_agent.set_tts_output(ElevenLabsTTS(voice="office_ai"))

                extracted_text += handler.extract_text(message["media"])
            message["content"] = extracted_text
            logging.info(f"File processed for {agent.staff_id}")

            audio_file = agent.generate_tts(reply_text)
            dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text, audio_file)
            logging.info(f"TTS + text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
        else:

            logging.info(f"Text sent to dashboard for {agent.staff_id}")
            
    except Exception as e:
        error_msg = f"Processing error for {agent.staff_id}: {str(e)}"
        logging.error(error_msg)
        sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
        whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
        email_notifier.send("Agent Processing Failure", error_msg)

# -------------------------------
# Step 6: Real-Time Monitoring Loop
# -------------------------------
def monitor_agents(interval_seconds=60):
    """
    Continuously monitor all cloned agents for failures
    Runs every interval_seconds, triggers instant notifications on errors
    """
    logging.info("Starting real-time monitoring loop...")
    
    while True:
        for staff_name, agent in staff_agents.items():
            try:
                # SDK method: check agent health/status
                status = agent.check_health()  # returns 'ok' or error string
                if status != "ok":

            except Exception as e:
                error_msg = f"Monitoring exception for {staff_name}: {str(e)}"
                logging.error(error_msg)
                sms_notifier.send(error_msg)
                whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
                email_notifier.send("Monitoring Failure", error_msg)
        
        time.sleep(interval_seconds)

# -------------------------------
# Step 7: Start Monitoring (Optional Thread)
# -------------------------------
import threading
monitor_thread = threading.Thread(target=monitor_agents, args=(60,), daemon=True)
monitor_thread.start()
logging.info("Real-time monitoring thread started.")

ssing with Escalation
